If the empty block bothers you (as it does me), make more assertions:

catch (SomeException e) {
    assertTrue(&quot;offending field not included in error
message&quot;,e.getMessage().indexof(&quot;badfield&quot;) != -1);
}

Typically when something&#39;s gone wrong, I want to be sure there&#39;s some
particular piece of information in the output anyway.

-Kevin
